&lt;b&gt;- Where are we today?&lt;/b&gt;
We use a patched Gold, a patched ar, a gold plugin in order to produce .pexe or .pso

&lt;b&gt;- Why is this a problem?&lt;/b&gt;
If we can get rid of gold for bitcode linking, a lot of things will become simple.

&lt;b&gt;- The proposed enhancement:&lt;/b&gt;
Implement the bitcode-level linker based on lib/Linker.

&lt;b&gt;- Exit criteria:&lt;/b&gt;
Gold is not used for linking .pexe/.pso.


&lt;b&gt;- Anticipated impact:&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;b&gt;[for users as well as other parts of the system]&lt;/b&gt;
